{"lemma":"شَحْمِ","slug":"شَحْمِ","root":"ش.ح.م","root_slug":"ش-ح-م","root_link":"/words/roots/ش-ح-م","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":6,"pos_tags":["adj","noun","verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":10},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n21838","n21840","n21841","n21842"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B4%D9%8E%D8%AD%D9%92%D9%85%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of شَحَمَ (šaḥama) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"grease, fat, lard, suet, schmaltz; also greasy pulp like of the colocynth or pomegranate"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be desirous of (eating) fat (of a person)"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to become plump and full (of fruit)"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be fat, to become fat (of a person)"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to feed fat"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to become desirous of fat"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to grease, to smear with fat, to oil"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"desirous of fat"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"pappy, mushy, of a texture resembling fat"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n21838","headword_ar":"شَحُمَ","root":"$Hm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aHaAmapN","text_ar":"شَحَامَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (MA, Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a man, S, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, fat;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, MA, K;) as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aHima","text_ar":"شَحِمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, abundant in the fat of his person."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aHumato A_ibiluhu","text_ar":"شَحُمَتْ اـِبِلُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His camels were,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, fat."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$uHimati Aln~aAqapu","text_ar":"شُحِمَتِ النَّاقَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aHamat","text_ar":"شَحَمَت"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"; of the classes of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuniYa","text_ar":"عُنِىَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naSara","text_ar":"نَصَرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aHomN","text_ar":"شَحْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$uHuwmN","text_ar":"شُحُومٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":";"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The she-camel became fat after leanness."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aHima","text_ar":"شَحِمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aHamN","text_ar":"شَحَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, eagerly desirous of fat."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, TA.) And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He ate much fat."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aHamahu","text_ar":"شَحَمَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aHama A^aSoHaAbahu","text_ar":"شَحَمَ اَصْحَابَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aHomN","text_ar":"شَحْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He fed him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his companions, with fat;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gave him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"them, fat to eat."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Msb","K","MA","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n21840","headword_ar":"شَحْمٌ","root":"$Hm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, K,) of an animal, (Msb,) a word of well known meaning, (S, Msb, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Fat;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(MA, KL;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the substance of fatness:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISd, TA:)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aHomapN","text_ar":"شَحْمَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a more special term, (S, Msb,) [i. e. a n. un.,] signifying"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a piece thereof:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) the pl. of the former is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$uHuwmN","text_ar":"شُحُومٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb, TA.) It is said of the Jews, in a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Harumato Ealayohimu Al$~uHuwmu fabaAEuwhaA","text_ar":"حَرُمَتْ عَلَيْهِمُ الشُّحُومُ فَبَاعُوهَا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waA^akaluwA A^avomaAnahaA","text_ar":"وَاَكَلُوا اَثْمَانَهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Fats have been forbidden to them; but they have sold them, and have devoured the prices thereof:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see Lev. vii. 23]: the fat that is forbidden to them is that of the kidneys and of the stomach and of the intestines into which the food passes from the stomach; but not that of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^alayop","text_ar":"اَلَيْة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[meaning the “ rump, ” and also the “ tail of a sheep, ”] nor of the back. (TA.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laqiytuhu bi$aHomi kulaAhu","text_ar":"لَقِيتُهُ بِشَحْمِ كُلَاهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[lit."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I met him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"found him, with the fat of his kidneys,"},{"kind":"text","text":"] meaning, (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in his state of briskness, liveliness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sprightliness."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.) And of him who is deemed weak, one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN $aHomN lilomubotaliEi","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ شَحْمٌ لِلْمُبْتَلِعِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  [lit."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one is fat for the swallower"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Ham p. 771.) ―         -b2-  Also The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hump of the camel:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) heard by Az from the Arabs in this sense. (TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hm","text_ar":"حم"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b3-  And The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"whiteness"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app. meaning the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"white part"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the belly."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aHomapu AlA^u*uni","text_ar":"شَحْمَةُ الاُذُنِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The lobe,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lobule, of the ear;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the part, of the ear, to which the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"quroT","text_ar":"قُرْط"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ear-ring"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ear-drop"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"is suspended;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K;) i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the soft portion of the lower part of the ear:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the place of the perforation for the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"quroT","text_ar":"قُرْط"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aHomapu AlEayoni","text_ar":"شَحْمَةُ العَيْنِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muqolap","text_ar":"مُقْلَة"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the eye;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;) i. e.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what comprises the white and the black of the eye:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Zj in his “ Khalk el-Insán; ” and S and Msb and K voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muqolapN","text_ar":"مُقْلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":":) [this is what is generally meant by it; i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the globe of the eye:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] in the T it is said to be"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hadaqap","text_ar":"حَدَقَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"black,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what is in the middle of the white,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the eye:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and some say that it is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aHomap","text_ar":"شَحْمَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app. meaning the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"whole substance"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that is beneath"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"behind"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hadaqap","text_ar":"حَدَقَة"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aHomapu","text_ar":"شَحْمَةُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlHanoZali","text_ar":"الحَنْظَلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aHomuhu","text_ar":"شَحْمُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", as in the K in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HnZl","text_ar":"حنظل"},{"kind":"text","text":",]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The inner part"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e. the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pulp"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the colocynth, exclusive of its seeds."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b7-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aHomapu Alr~um~aAni","text_ar":"شَحْمَةُ الرُّمَّانِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The thin yellow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pulp"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that is amid the seeds of the pomegranate;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K;) or, as in the M,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the substance that separates the seeds of the pomegranate."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b8-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aHomu Aln~axoli","text_ar":"شَحْمُ النَّخْلِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The heart pith,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cerebrum,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jum~aAr","text_ar":"جُمَّار"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of palm-trees:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"j*b","text_ar":"جذب"},{"kind":"text","text":":) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aHomapu Aln~axolapi","text_ar":"شَحْمَةُ النَّخْلَةِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the heart"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jum~aArap","text_ar":"جُمَّارَة"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the palm-tree."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, TA.) ―         -b9-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aHomapu Almaroji","text_ar":"شَحْمَةُ المَرْجِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xiTomiY~","text_ar":"خِطْمِىّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"marsh-mallow"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (K.) ―         -b10-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aHomu AlA^aroDi","text_ar":"شَحْمُ الاَرْضِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The truffle;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as a gen. n.; syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alkamo'u","text_ar":"الكَمْءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kmA^","text_ar":"كما"},{"kind":"text","text":":) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aHomapu AlA^aroDi","text_ar":"شَحْمَةُ الاَرْضِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the truffle;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as a n. un.; syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlkamoA^apu","text_ar":"الكَمْاَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the white truffle;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlkamoA^apu AlbayoDaA='u","text_ar":"الكَمْاَةُ البَيْضَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S.) [It should be observed that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alkamo'u","text_ar":"الكَمْءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is generally held to be a n. un.; and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlkamoA^apu","text_ar":"الكَمْاَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", to be a coll. gen. n.; contr. to analogy: but they are here evidently used in the reverse manner.] ―         -b11-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aHomapu AlA^aroDi","text_ar":"شَحْمَةُ الاَرْضِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A certain white worm:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"min","text_ar":"مِن"},{"kind":"text","text":"[which is omitted in some of the copies of the K])"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"long worms, found in moist earth, and in the mud of rivers, called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaraATiyn","text_ar":"خَرَاطِين"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a white"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaZaA='ap","text_ar":"عَظَا=ءَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[n. un. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaZaA='N","text_ar":"عَظَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not big:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or, as some say, it is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not of the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"species called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaZaA='","text_ar":"عَظَا=ء"},{"kind":"text","text":";"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it is more pleasant"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to the taste"},{"kind":"text","text":"],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and better: and"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"because it dwells in the sand-hills,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"they say"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"call it"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aHomapu","text_ar":"شَحْمَةُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aln~aqaA","text_ar":"النَّقَا"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"like as they say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"banaAtu Aln~aqaA","text_ar":"بَنَاتُ النَّقَا"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) it is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"reptile called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hulakap","text_ar":"حُلَكَة"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which dives into the sand, and to which the fingers"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"banaAn","text_ar":"بَنَان"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of virgins are likened."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ArD","text_ar":"ارض"},{"kind":"text","text":". [See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HulakapN","text_ar":"حُلَكَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and see also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$abavN","text_ar":"شَبَثٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) ―         -b12-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^abuw $aHomK","text_ar":"اَبُو شَحْمٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is an appellation of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The small species of what is called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HimaAru qab~aAna","text_ar":"حِمَارُ قَبَّانَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qb","text_ar":"قب"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.) ―         -b13-  [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aHomapN","text_ar":"شَحْمَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"below.]"}],"source_refs":["S","Msb","K","ISd","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n21841","headword_ar":"شُحْمٌ","root":"$Hm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", with damm, [as though pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^a$oHamu","text_ar":"اَشْحَمُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which I do not find mentioned,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"White;"},{"kind":"text","text":"applied to men. (IAar, TA.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n21842","headword_ar":"شَحِمٌ","root":"$Hm","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Eagerly desirous of fat."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajulN $aHimN laHimN","text_ar":"رَجُلٌ شَحِمٌ لَحِمٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A man eagerly desirous of fat and of flesh."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EinabN $aHimN","text_ar":"عِنَبٌ شَحِمٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Grapes having little juice"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and thick skin."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rum~aAnapN $aHimapN","text_ar":"رُمَّانَةٌ شَحِمَةٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A pomegranate having thick"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aHomap","text_ar":"شَحْمَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pulp amid the seeds"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["K","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}